# CocoaPods; define the repository policy before adding it.

## Carthage
Carthage/Build/

## fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png
fastlane/test_output

## macOS
.DS_Store

## Tooling and local environment
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.log
